body:
We have managed to figure how to solve the problem but not sure of it's cause.

Solution surprising simple and wierd

The problem occur when we have this pattern:

```golang
if err := <-errChan; err != nil {
	defer Foobar()
	logrus.WithFields(logrus.Fields{}).Error("")
	return nil, whatever
} else {
....
}
```

And this fixes it

```golang
if err := <-errChan; err != nil {
	logrus.WithFields(logrus.Fields{}).Error("")
	defer Foobar()
	return nil, whatever
} else {
....
}
```
i.e. just changing the position of the `defer` statement.
